usage: validate_config.py [-h] --config-dir CONFIG_DIR [--policy POLICY]
                          [--rule-packs RULE_PACKS] [--version-check] [--json]
                          [--policy-dsl POLICY_DSL]

One-stop configuration validation

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --config-dir CONFIG_DIR
                        Path to tenant config directory (conf.d/)
  --policy POLICY       Path to policy YAML (allowed_domains etc.)
  --rule-packs RULE_PACKS
                        Path to rule-packs/ directory for custom rule lint
  --version-check       Also run version consistency check
  --json                Output results as JSON (for CI consumption)
  --policy-dsl POLICY_DSL
                        Path to standalone Policy-as-Code DSL file (top-level
                        policies: key)
